# Dependency directories (මේක අනිවාර්යයෙන්ම ඕනේ)
node_modules/

# Environment variables (Database credentials/ports සේරම තියෙන්නේ මෙතන හින්දා මේක අනිවාර්යයි)
.env
.env.local
.env.*.local

# Logs
logs
*.log
npm-debug.log*

# Diagnostic reports (Crashed templates)
report.[0-9]*.[0-9]*.[0-9]*.[0-9]*.json

# Runtime data
pids
*.pid
*.seed
*.pid.lock

# Directory for instrumented libs generated by jscoverage/JSCover
lib-cov

# Coverage directory used by tools like istanbul
coverage
*.lcov

# IDEs and editors
.class
.project
.settings/
.idea/
.vscode/